OL,3,CWorking from home 'not proper work,'
OL,4,Cex-Asda and M&S boss says
OL,6,FRemote working became widespread
OL,7,Fduring the Covid-19 lockdowns, with
OL,8,Fthe number of people working from home
OL,9,Fmore than doubling from 4.7 million in
OL,10,Flate 2019 to 9.9 million by early 2022.
OL,12,FThe latest official figures show that
OL,13,F28% of the UK workforce now works in a
OL,14,Fhybrid model, 13% work fully remotely,
OL,15,Fand 44% commute to a workplace.
OL,17,FBut recently a growing number of
OL,18,Fcompanies including Amazon, Boots and
OL,19,FJP Morgan have called their employees
OL,20,Fback to the office to work full-time.
