OL,3,CWorking from home 'not proper work,'
OL,4,Cex-Asda and M&S boss says
OL,6,FLord Rose called Asda's 5,000-strong
OL,7,Fteam of head office workers back to
OL,8,Fthe office for at least three days a
OL,9,Fweek in 2024.
OL,11,FA biography of the former chief on
OL,12,FAsda's website says: "Stuart appears
OL,13,Fto have no hobbies apart from work and
OL,14,Fhas a dog called Bruce."
