OL,3,CWorking from home 'not proper work,'
OL,4,Cex-Asda and M&S boss says
OL,6,FRebecca Florisson, principal analyst
OL,7,Fat the Work Foundation at Lancaster
OL,8,FUniversity called the recent rollback
OL,9,Fon hybrid and remote work "unhelpful".
OL,11,F"For many workers, remote work is not
OL,12,Fa 'nice to have' but a key element to
OL,13,Ftheir ability to get into and remain
OL,14,Fin work. Disabled workers have
OL,15,Findicated that working from home
OL,16,Fallows them to better manage their
OL,17,Fcondition and report maintained or
OL,18,Fimproved productivity.
